#: /tmp/build-i2p/apps/routerconsole/java/build/../../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/router/web/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:505
msgid ""
"Your I2P+ router by default contributes to the network by routing internal, "
"end-to-end encrypted traffic for other routers, known as "
"<i>participation</i>. Bandwidth participation improves the anonymity level "
"of all users on the network and maximizes your download speed."
msgstr ""
"Vaš strežnik I2P+ privzeto prispeva k omrežju tako, da usmerja notranji, "
"šifrirani promet od konca do konca za druge strežnike, znane kot "
"<i>sodelovanje</i>. Sodelovanje v širini pasma izboljša ravni anonimnosti "
"vseh uporabnikov v omrežju in doseže maksimalno hitrost prenosov"

#: /tmp/build-i2p/apps/routerconsole/java/build/../../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/router/web/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:507
msgid ""
"For the best experience, it's recommended to configure your bandwidth "
"settings to match the values provided by your ISP. If you are unsure of your"
" bandwidth, you can run a test to determine your download and upload speeds."
msgstr ""
"Za najboljšo izkušnjo je priporočljivo, da konfigurirate nastavitve širine "
"pasma, da se ujemajo z vrednostmi, ki jih pruža vaš ISP. Če niste prepričani"
" o vaši širini pasma, lahko poženete test, da določite vaše hitrosti prenosa"
" in nalaganja"

#: /tmp/build-i2p/apps/routerconsole/java/build/../../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/router/web/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:511
msgid "Bandwidth Test"
msgstr "Test širine pasma"

#: /tmp/build-i2p/apps/routerconsole/java/build/../../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/router/web/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:515
msgid ""
"I2P+ will now test your internet connection to identify the optimal speed "
"settings."
msgstr ""
"I2P+ zdaj preveri vaše omrežje interneta, da določi optimalne nastavitve "
"hitrosti"

#: /tmp/build-i2p/apps/routerconsole/java/build/../../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/router/web/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:517
msgid "This is done using the third-party M-Lab service."
msgstr "To se izvede z uporabo storitve tretjega stranka M-Lab."

#: /tmp/build-i2p/apps/routerconsole/java/build/../../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/router/web/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:523
msgid "Please review the M-Lab privacy policies linked below."
msgstr "Prosimo, da preglejete politike zasebnosti M-Lab, povezane spodaj."

#: /tmp/build-i2p/apps/routerconsole/java/build/../../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/router/web/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:525
msgid ""
"If you do not wish to run the M-Lab bandwidth test, you may skip it by "
"clicking the button below."
msgstr ""
"Če ne želite poženeti testa širine pasma M-Lab, ga lahko preskočite tako, da"
" kliknete gumb spodaj"

#: /tmp/build-i2p/apps/routerconsole/java/build/../../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/router/web/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:532
msgid "M-Lab Privacy Policy"
msgstr "Politika zasebnosti M-Lab"

#: /tmp/build-i2p/apps/routerconsole/java/build/../../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/router/web/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:535
msgid "M-Lab Name Server Privacy Policy"
msgstr "Politika zasebnosti imenski strežnik M-Lab"

#: /tmp/build-i2p/apps/routerconsole/java/build/../../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/router/web/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:545
msgid ""
"The bandwidth test is now running and will take around 60 seconds to "
"complete, after which you should be forwarded to the results page."
msgstr ""
"Test širine pasma zdaj teče in potrebuje približno 60 sekund za končanje, po"
" katerem se morate preusmeriti na stran z rezultati"

#: /tmp/build-i2p/apps/routerconsole/java/build/../../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/router/web/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:547
msgid "Bandwidth Test in progress"
msgstr "Test širine pasma v teku"

#: /tmp/build-i2p/apps/routerconsole/java/build/../../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/router/web/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:549
msgid ""
"Javascript is disabled - wait 60 seconds for the bandwidth test to complete "
"and then click Next"
msgstr ""
"Javascript je onemogočen - počakajte 60 sekund, da se test širine pasma "
"zaključi, in nato kliknite Napre"

#: /tmp/build-i2p/apps/routerconsole/java/build/../../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/router/web/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:569
msgid "Bandwidth Test Results"
msgstr "Rezultati testa širine pasma"

