msgid "Bandwidth Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija širine pasma"

#: /tmp/build-i2p/apps/routerconsole/java/build/../../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/router/web/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:682
#, java-format
msgid "You have configured I2P+ to share only {0} KBps."
msgstr "Konfigurirali ste I2P, da deli le {0} KBps."

#: /tmp/build-i2p/apps/routerconsole/java/build/../../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/router/web/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:684
msgid "I2P+ requires at least 12KBps to enable sharing. "
msgstr "I2P zahteva vsaj 12KBps za omogočanje deljenja."

#: /tmp/build-i2p/apps/routerconsole/java/build/../../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/router/web/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:688
#, java-format
msgid "You have configured I2P+ to share {0} KBps."
msgstr "Konfigurirali ste I2P za deljenje {0} KBps."

#: /tmp/build-i2p/apps/routerconsole/java/build/../../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/router/web/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:702
msgid ""
"I2P+ requires a web browser configured to use the resident HTTP proxy in "
"order to browse websites on the I2P network."
msgstr ""
"I2P+ zahteva spletni brskalnik, konfiguriran za uporabo bivalčega HTTP "
"posredniškega strežnika, da lahko brskate po spletnih straneh na omrežju I2P"

#: /tmp/build-i2p/apps/routerconsole/java/build/../../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/router/web/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:706
msgid "Browser Setup"
msgstr "Nastavitev brskalnika"

#: /tmp/build-i2p/apps/routerconsole/java/build/../../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/router/web/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:710
msgid ""
"In order to access websites hosted on the I2P network, and optionally use "
"the default outproxy to connect to websites on clearnet, you will need to "
"configure your browser to use the I2P+ <b>HTTP</b> proxy, by default running"
" on <code>127.0.0.1 port 4444</code>. "
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do spletnih strani, gostitvenih v omrežju I2P, in po možnosti za "
"uporabo privzeti outproxy za povezovanje na spletiših mestih na clearnetu, "
"morate konfigurirati svoj brskalnik za uporabo I2P+ <b>HTTP</b> proxy, ki se"
" privzeto izvaja na <code>127.0.0.1 port 4444</code>"

#: /tmp/build-i2p/apps/routerconsole/java/build/../../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/router/web/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:723
msgid "Welcome to I2P+!"
msgstr "Dobrodošli v I2P+!"

#: /tmp/build-i2p/apps/routerconsole/java/build/../../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/router/web/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:725
msgid ""
"When you start I2P+, it may take a few minutes to bootstrap (integrate) your"
" router into the network and find additional peers, so please be patient."
msgstr ""
"Ko zagnate I2P, lahko potrebuje nekaj minut za ujemanje (integracija) vašega"
" strežnika v omrežje in iskanje dodatnih sosednjih strežnikov, zato prosim, "
"da budete strpelni"

#: /tmp/build-i2p/apps/routerconsole/java/build/../../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/router/web/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:727
msgid ""
"Once green stars are indicated next to your Service Tunnels, there is a wide"
" variety of things you can do with I2P+."
msgstr ""
"Ko se vedo zelenih zvezdic poleg vaših tunelovih storitev, obstaja veliko "
"različnih stvari, ki jih lahko naredite z I2P+"

